--- Complete Streaming-Aware Compaction Implementation ---

This patch implements the streaming-aware compaction system with:
1. Stream state tracking in Engine
2. Deferred compaction when streaming active  
3. Post-compaction context restoration prompts
4. Integration with both sync and async worker paths

